overview: Nani and Dadi's close-knit family suffers some financial constraints. And with two unmarried granddaughters, their future appears bleak. But all is about to change when their brother-in-law calls to informs them that his son Ali, is visiting Pakistan to look for a life mate! Originally aired on GEO Entertainment in Pakistan. This is an Urdu language tele-film with English subtitles.
title: Tu Mera Chaand
